      "text": [
        " : نَهَى رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ أَنْ يَطْرُقَ اَلرَّجُلُ أَهْلَهُ لَيْلاً إِذَا جَاءَ مِنَ اَلْغَيْبَةِ حَتَّى يُؤْذِنَهُمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2514 - It is narrated from Jabir ibn Abdullah al-Ansari, who said:\nThe Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings of Allah (swt) be upon him and his family) forbade a man from entering upon his family at night when returning from a journey, until he informs them beforehand."
        ]
      }
